title: Navigon Mobile Navigator 731.137 Q4
description:
MobileNavigator 7 for Windows Mobile PDA and Smart Phones (Windows Mobile 5 / 6 / 6.1) 

Intuitive user interface
Precise audio instructions
Free map view
Reality View Pro (only available in landscape format)
Text to speech - Road names in route descriptions and navigation instructions are announced by the system1
Lane Assistant Pro
Importing of contact addresses from Outlook
Quickest, shortest and ideal route
Real  Signpost  Display
Speed  Assistant
"Go home" function
2D/3D view
Planning multi-leg routes
Door-to-door navigation
Logbook
Free TMC reception (2)
POIs on the route
Speed camera information (3) (speed camera information is not permitted in all countries. Please check the legal situation in the country you are travelling in)
More free functions (4)
- Weather service - 3-day weather forecasts
- HRS (Hotel Reservation System) - find and book hotels

1available in the following countries: Austria, France, UK, Germany, Ireland, Italy, Netherlands, Portugal, Spain, Sweden, Liechtenstein, Belgium, Luxemburg, Switzerland

(2) not available in all countries


(3) speed camera information is not permitted in all countries. Please check the legal situation in the country you are travelling in


(4) Depending on your chosen tariff, you may be charged for data connections.
